ki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aauminki</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/con's RED</span><br>  Posts: 393<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/24/02 2:09:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=3>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Faction Farms?</span><hr size=1> The best +Coldain faction that I've seen is the Frost Giant manor in Kael, in order of size of hit I would rate the different zones like this:<br><br>GD (low hits, I wouldn't bother)<br>EW (better hits, still will take a bit to get faction)<br>Kael (Giants with beards are Rif or Frost Giants, those are the largest hits to +Coldain)<br><br>I went from Max Scowls -&gt; Indifferent in two days of about 4-5 hour sessions killing the rif giants in Kael, it's really not so hard that some people crank it up to be - I'm raising faction solely for getting the Coldain Ring (got the 8th now). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubrutultarewmarr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brutul Tarew Marr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 189<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/24/02 10:39:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.blackcompany.cc/member_pics/45.jpg height=185 width=100></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Faction Farms?</span><hr size=1> Coldain is pretty easy to get, just from killing bearded giants whereever.  A tormax hit is about the only way to go for Dain, although one guy on our server actually collected 1500 small velium pieces and did the pick sharpening quest 1500 times to get Dain faction.  I don't think I'd reccomend that though <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6629>Brutul Vilesilencer</a><br>Barbarian Warlord of the <a href=http://www.blackcompany.cc>Black Company</a><br>Tarew Marr</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uaerildroigheann.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aeril Droigheann</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>/con's RED</span><br>  Posts: 323<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/27/02 7:56:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Faction Farms?</span><hr size=1> Zek have beards, they're just trimmed. :P<br><br>The arena is pretty much all Zek so that wouldn't give a coldain hit.  The best area is Iceshard Keep, past the fishing pond. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=45589">Aeryl Firebrand</a>, Warlord<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=65788">Aeril Droigheann</a>, 59 Preserver, Semi-Retired<br><a href="http://berglad.stormloader.com/">Undaunted</a>, Xegony<br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uswanda08.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Swanda08</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/28/02 1:12:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Faction Farms?</span><hr size=1> be the puller for an AE group in Great divide, that works too.. <br>btw i dont get why you dont convince your guild to go Giant.. :P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uaauminki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aauminki</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will KICK YOUR @$$</span><br>  Posts: 407<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/28/02 1:56:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=7>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Faction Farms?</span><hr size=1> We killed Dain sometime last week, and I went to dubious with Coldain. Spent yesterday at the manor in Kael, got about 200 +Coldain faction hits which raised my faction back to Ally - I'd guess each rif giant in KD is worth an average of 10 points of Coldain faction - totally uneducated guess would be:<br><br>GD - 1pt<br>EW - 5pt<br>KD - 10pt<br><br>Just my hunch, take it for what it's worth <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> . <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/unamuras.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Namuras</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/28/02 7:46:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Faction Farms?</span><hr size=1> The Elites in GD also give 10 pts. There are also a couple named in the fort that I'm sure give extra points. Riff House in KD is by far the best place to get Dorf faction. I just changed from Giant to CoV/Coldain myself and it took 3 Arena raids to get to Warmly to CoV and numerous hours in GD killing them. The good thing is that I was getting exp for my Drood also as he was 45 when I acquired him, so I was accomplishing 2 things at once.<br><br>Namuras<br>55 Myrmidon<br>Xev server <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showPrevMessage?topicID=486.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showNextMessage?topicID=486.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=486.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.emailToFriend?topicID=486.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.threadControl?topicID=486.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=486.topic>Subscribe</